msgctxt "136_Momiyama"
msgid "Wow, you sure are used to getting massages... Thanks to that, I was able to chisel away at your tense body like the great Michelangelo! How'd it feel, hmm?"
msgstr "Wow, you sure are used to getting massages... Thanks to that, I was able to chisel away at your tense body like the great Michelangelo! How'd it feel, hmm?"

msgctxt "148_Player"
msgid "It was great."
msgstr "It was great."

msgctxt "160_Momiyama"
msgid "Hehe, well, thanks!. I'll walk you out, then!"
msgstr "Hehe, well, thanks!. I'll walk you out, then!"

msgctxt "220_Momiyama"
msgid "Thank you so much for today! Come by again soon. I'll be waiting for you!"
msgstr "Thank you so much for today! Come by again soon. I'll be waiting for you!"

msgctxt "256_Player"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "268_Momiyama"
msgid "Wow, I never thought you'd get that into my massage, hehehe. But I won't be able to give you a massage worthy of your divine body if you don't relax more."
msgstr "Wow, I never thought you'd get that into my massage, hehehe. But I won't be able to give you a massage worthy of your divine body if you don't relax more."

