msgstr "......"

msgctxt "316_Momiyama"
msgid "You were fast asleep! I don't know whether to be offended or embarrassed. Was something wrong with the massage, or is it because I'm not some voluptuous vixen?"
msgstr "You were fast asleep! I don't know whether to be offended or embarrassed. Was something wrong with the massage, or is it because I'm not some voluptuous vixen?"

msgctxt "328_Player"
msgid "No, that's not it..."
msgstr "No, that's not it..."

msgctxt "340_Momiyama"
msgid "Oh, really? Ugh, that's such a relief! I don't know very many masterpieces like you who actually prefer a male therapist over a female therapist!"
msgstr "Oh, really? Ugh, that's such a relief! I don't know very many masterpieces like you who actually prefer a male therapist over a female therapist!"

msgctxt "352_Player"
msgid "Huh? No, that's not..."
msgstr "Huh? No, that's not..."

msgctxt "364_Momiyama"
msgid "Gosh, you should've told me that before! I know it's high fashion to be a real tease, but you didn't have to torture me like that. My poor heart was this close to breaking!"
msgstr "Gosh, you should've told me that before! I know it's high fashion to be a real tease, but you didn't have to torture me like that. My poor heart was this close to breaking!"

